<problem id="fs-id1167793380150">
<para id="fs-id1167793380152">Identify and create a graph of the conic section described by the equation</para>
<equation id="fs-id1167793380155" class="unnumbered"><label/><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>0.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>sin</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>θ</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
